{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no word, but I assume my mother was among the same people because both my sister and my mother worked at a place called the Siemens factories, which I know have a very prominent position in the United States today.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's an electronic company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I don't have any Siemens razor in my house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [INAUDIBLE] So-- so I-- I was kind of upset about the wording of this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wrote Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dole who was the president of the Red Cross at that time a letter and objected to this kind of-- you know, if you find out these things, why don't you tell it as it is.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not evacuated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were deported, you know, and-- to a-- to a death camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got a nice letter back from some lady who was told by Mrs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dole to answer me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the explanation was that's the wording the German Red Cross used.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they must apologize I took it so hard and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we-- we-- we did exactly what the German wrote.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just put it into English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, well, what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what I found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My sister was officially deported in March of 1943, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tell me what happened-- tell me the circumstances under-- under which you went-- well, when you went to Denmark, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Henry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Henry Kahan, K-A-H-A-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know what we were going to do in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought, like, we were going to go to school or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had a wakening up after about we spent a couple of days in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
